Kenya Microfinance Institutions Collect 9.1 Billion Shillings

-- B y   S a r a h   M c G r e g o r
-- 
2011-09-16T06:20:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/kenya-microfinance-institutions-collect-9-1-billion-shillings.html
Six deposit-taking microfinance
institutions in  Kenya  collected customer savings totalling 9.1
billion shillings ($96 million) since they were licensed by the
central bank three years ago, Governor Njuguna Ndung’u said.  “That has been a market waiting to be discovered,”
Ndung’u told reporters today in Nairobi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah McGregor in Nairobi at 
 smcgregor5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  